o record rollout items: thread 019dd1c9-c6a3-71b3-b439-18a026bc92ba not found`, and the preserved branch still lacks the discovered `3.0.0` URL/description fields in `metadata/io.zipkin.reporter2/zipkin-reporter/index.json`.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Restore or regenerate `tests/src/io.zipkin.reporter2/zipkin-reporter/3.0.0`, then apply the `zipkin2.reporter.*` import/signature fixes described near the end of `pi-generation-2026-04-28T01-56-28-310260Z.log`.\n2. Re-apply the `index.json` updates from `human-intervention-logs/io.zipkin.reporter2:zipkin-reporter:3.0.0/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log`.\n3. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.zipkin.reporter2:zipkin-reporter:3.0.0` and preserve the actual source changes, not only the logs."}}
